  "time_ut": 1660890780,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dbd\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0da7\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca 209\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd \u0daf\u0dd3 \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Paddy Marketing Board buys 209 tonnes of Paddy",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The rice marketing board started the purchase of paddy harvest in the yala season from yesterday (18). Accordingly, the marketing board buys Nadu paddy for 120 rupees, samba paddy for 125 rupees and Keeri samba paddy for 130 rupees.",
        "Under this, 55 warehouses belonging to the Rice Marketing Board were opened yesterday to buy paddy from the farmers in several districts that have been harvested and those that are currently being harvested.",
        "Mr. Mahinda Amaraweera, the Minister of Agriculture, Wildlife and Forest Resources Conservation, says that the Chairman of the Paddy Marketing Board has informed that yesterday two hundred and nine thousand six hundred kilograms of paddy was purchased by the rice warehouses belonging to the Paddy Marketing Board of Ampara District, Anuradhapura District and the Northern Region.",
        "Today (19) in the morning, the Minister inquired about the progress of the rice purchase activities from Mr. Neil de Alwis, Chairman of the Rice Marketing Board.",
        "The minister also instructed to further increase the number of warehouses open to buy paddy today.",
        "According to the Chairman of the Rice Marketing Board, 75-100 warehouses will be opened for purchasing rice today. Also, there are plans to expand the warehouses according to the areas where rice is harvested.",
        "In many parts of the island, paddy harvesting has already started in the yala season. Therefore, due to the rapid decline in the price of a kilo of paddy in the market, some businessmen are working to buy the paddy harvest of the farmers.",
        "Due to that situation, the Paddy Marketing Board took steps to buy paddy by giving a minimum price for a kilo of paddy.",
        "The marketing board has planned to expand the PMB Rice production activities in the coming period as per the instructions of the Minister of Agriculture."
      ],
